<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_client_script"><sys_ux_client_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><controller_preset/><includes/><macroponent display_value="Dashboards">4ba7aa7f9360b29005087efdfaba10a9</macroponent><name>Navigate to dashboard scheduled export</name><preset/><required_translations>[]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[/**
* @param {params} params
* @param {api} params.api
* @param {any} params.event
* @param {any} params.imports
* @param {ApiHelpers} params.helpers
*/
function handler({api, event, helpers, imports}) {
    api.emit('NAV_ITEM_SELECTED', {
        route: 'scheduled-export',
        icon: 'calendar-days-clock-outline',
        title: 'Scheduled Export',
         fields: {
            sysId:'new' + Date.now(),
        },
        params: {
            dashboardId: event.payload.dashboardSysId,
        }
    });
}]]></script><script_api_version>2.0.0</script_api_version><sys_class_name>sys_ux_client_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2025-10-19 17:22:20</sys_created_on><sys_id>0fa722bf9360b29005087efdfaba1081</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Navigate to dashboard scheduled export</sys_name><sys_package display_value="NowRoom" source="x_1782765_nowroom">699b40c09340761005087efdfaba109b</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="NowRoom">699b40c09340761005087efdfaba109b</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_client_script_0fa722bf9360b29005087efdfaba1081</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2025-10-19 17:22:20</sys_updated_on><target>macroponent</target><type>default</type></sys_ux_client_script></record_update>
